---
import FunnelLayout from '../layouts/FunnelLayout.astro';

const supportEmail = 'hello@fengtalk.ai';
---

<FunnelLayout title="Domain Setup - ProfitsLocal" description="Domain and subdomain setup instructions">
  <section class="domain-shell">
    <p class="eyebrow">Domain setup</p>
    <h1>Choose the launch address before we publish live.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      The dev preview stays available for approval and revisions. The public live site needs one clear address.
      Some options are handled by us; others require a DNS change from your domain manager.
    </p>

    <div class="current-panel" data-current-panel hidden>
      <span>Current request</span>
      <h2 data-current-domain></h2>
      <p data-current-copy></p>
      <dl>
        <div data-client-row hidden><dt>Client</dt><dd data-client></dd></div>
        <div data-target-row hidden><dt>Pages target</dt><dd data-target></dd></div>
        <div data-preview-row hidden><dt>Dev preview</dt><dd><a data-preview target="_blank"></a></dd></div>
      </dl>
    </div>

    <div class="domain-grid">
      <article>
        <span>Default / no customer DNS</span>
        <h2>Free ProfitsLocal subdomain</h2>
        <p>Use a dedicated address under our domain, such as <strong>yourbusiness.profitslocal.com</strong>.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>You do not log in to a registrar.</li>
          <li>We create the DNS record and attach it to the approved live Pages project.</li>
          <li>Best for fast launch, QR codes, menus, and outreach links.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="record-box" data-free-record hidden>
          <strong>For this order</strong>
          <code data-free-domain></code>
          <small>We must configure this before it opens. If it does not resolve yet, it is pending setup or certificate validation.</small>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article>
        <span>Customer DNS / safest</span>
        <h2>Your subdomain</h2>
        <p>Use a focused address, such as <strong>menu.yourbusiness.com</strong> or <strong>order.yourbusiness.com</strong>.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Best if you already have an official website.</li>
          <li>Customer adds one CNAME record.</li>
          <li>We attach the custom domain in Cloudflare Pages after DNS resolves.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="record-box">
          <strong>DNS record</strong>
          <code><span data-subdomain-name>menu.yourbusiness.com</span> CNAME <span data-pages-target>your-project-live.pages.dev</span></code>
          <small>If your DNS is on Cloudflare, leave the record proxied or DNS-only according to your existing policy; the important part is the CNAME target.</small>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article>
        <span>Official replacement</span>
        <h2>Your root domain</h2>
        <p>Use your main website address, such as <strong>yourbusiness.com</strong>.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Best when this will replace your official website.</li>
          <li>Cloudflare DNS can use a flattened CNAME at the root.</li>
          <li>Other registrars may need ALIAS/ANAME, or use <strong>www.yourbusiness.com</strong> and redirect the root.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="record-box">
          <strong>Preferred DNS records</strong>
          <code>@ CNAME <span data-pages-target>your-project-live.pages.dev</span></code>
          <code>www CNAME <span data-pages-target>your-project-live.pages.dev</span></code>
          <small>Root domains are slower because we must avoid breaking existing email, website, or registrar settings.</small>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article>
        <span>Not the launch path yet</span>
        <h2>ProfitsLocal subpage</h2>
        <p>Use a path such as <strong>profitslocal.com/yourbusiness</strong>.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>No DNS change from the customer.</li>
          <li>Useful later for a directory, case study, or temporary listing.</li>
          <li>Not currently the production website launch route unless we build the root-site router.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="handoff-panel">
      <h2>What happens after approval</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>You approve the dev preview.</li>
        <li>We confirm the launch address and Pages project target.</li>
        <li>For a ProfitsLocal subdomain, we create DNS and attach the custom domain ourselves.</li>
        <li>For your own domain or subdomain, you add the DNS record or invite us to help.</li>
        <li>We wait for Cloudflare Pages domain status and HTTPS certificate to become active.</li>
        <li>We send the final live link. The preview utility pages remain available for revisions.</li>
      </ol>
      <a href={`mailto:${supportEmail}`}>{supportEmail}</a>
    </div>

    <div class="steps-panel">
      <h2>Rule of thumb</h2>
      <p><strong>Fastest:</strong> use our free <span data-client-subdomain>client.profitslocal.com</span> subdomain.</p>
      <p><strong>Best when you already have a website:</strong> use a customer subdomain like <strong>menu.yourbusiness.com</strong>.</p>
      <p><strong>Best for a full replacement:</strong> use the root domain after checking existing DNS, email, and website records.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</FunnelLayout>

<script>
  const params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
  const clientSlug = params.get('client_slug') || '';
  const requestedDomain = cleanDomain(params.get('domain') || params.get('preferred_domain') || '');
  const previewUrl = params.get('preview_url') || (clientSlug ? `https://${clientSlug}-dev.pages.dev` : '');
  const liveProject = clientSlug ? `${clientSlug}-live` : 'your-project-live';
  const pagesTarget = `${liveProject}.pages.dev`;
  const defaultSubdomain = clientSlug ? `${clientSlug}.profitslocal.com` : 'client.profitslocal.com';
  const selectedDomain = requestedDomain || defaultSubdomain;
  const route = classifyDomain(selectedDomain);

  setText('[data-pages-target]', pagesTarget);
  setText('[data-client-subdomain]', defaultSubdomain);
  setText('[data-subdomain-name]', route.kind === 'customer-subdomain' ? selectedDomain : 'menu.yourbusiness.com');

  const panel = document.querySelector('[data-current-panel]');
  if (panel && (clientSlug || selectedDomain || previewUrl)) {
    panel.hidden = false;
    setText('[data-current-domain]', selectedDomain);
    setText('[data-current-copy]', route.copy);
    setText('[data-client]', clientSlug || 'Not provided');
    setText('[data-target]', pagesTarget);
    showRow('[data-client-row]', Boolean(clientSlug));
    showRow('[data-target-row]', Boolean(clientSlug));
    const preview = document.querySelector('[data-preview]');
    if (preview && previewUrl) {
      preview.textContent = previewUrl;
      preview.href = previewUrl;
      showRow('[data-preview-row]', true);
    }
  }

  if (route.kind === 'profitslocal-subdomain') {
    const record = document.querySelector('[data-free-record]');
    if (record) record.hidden = false;
    setText('[data-free-domain]', `${selectedDomain} -> ${pagesTarget}`);
  }

  function classifyDomain(value) {
    const host = cleanDomain(value);
    if (!host) {
      return {
        kind: 'profitslocal-subdomain',
        copy: 'No domain was requested, so the fastest route is a free ProfitsLocal subdomain that we configure.',
      };
    }
    if (host === 'profitslocal.com' || host.endsWith('.profitslocal.com')) {
      return {
        kind: 'profitslocal-subdomain',
        copy: 'This is under our domain. We configure DNS and Cloudflare Pages; no customer DNS change is needed.',
      };
    }
    if (host.split('.').length > 2) {
      return {
        kind: 'customer-subdomain',
        copy: `Ask the domain manager to add a CNAME from ${host} to ${pagesTarget}.`,
      };
    }
    return {
      kind: 'customer-root',
      copy: `This is a root domain. We need to inspect existing DNS first, then choose Cloudflare flattened CNAME, ALIAS/ANAME, or www redirect.`,
    };
  }

  function cleanDomain(value) {
    return String(value || '')
      .trim()
      .replace(/^https?:\/\//i, '')
      .replace(/\/.*$/, '')
      .replace(/\.$/, '')
      .toLowerCase();
  }

  function setText(selector, value) {
    document.querySelectorAll(selector).forEach((node) => {
      node.textContent = value;
    });
  }

  function showRow(selector, show) {
    const row = document.querySelector(selector);
    if (row) row.hidden = !show;
  }
</script>

<style>
  .domain-shell {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem) 0;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: #b9802f;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
    color: #17120e;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.8rem);
    font-weight: 950;
    line-height: 0.92;
  }

  .lede {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    color: #665d55;
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .domain-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  article,
  .current-panel,
  .handoff-panel,
  .steps-panel {
    border: 1px solid #ddd6cc;
    background: #fffdf8;
    padding: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
  }

  .current-panel {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    background: #17120e;
    border-color: #17120e;
  }

  .current-panel span,
  article span {
    color: #b9802f;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .current-panel h2,
  .current-panel p,
  .current-panel dt,
  .current-panel dd,
  .current-panel a {
    color: #fffdf8;
  }

  dl {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
  }

  dt {
    color: #8e8378;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  dd {
    margin: 0.2rem 0 0;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
    color: #17120e;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }

  p,
  li {
    color: #665d55;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
  }

  .record-box {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.9rem;
    background: #f3eee6;
  }

  code {
    display: block;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
    color: #17120e;
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  small {
    color: #665d55;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .handoff-panel {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .steps-panel {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  ol {
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
  }

  .handoff-panel a {
    color: #17120e;
    font-weight: 950;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .domain-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    dl {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
